{"tid":2340983,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Apple Car首張圖片曝光","createTime":"2020-12-26T03:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T19:23:40.000Z","uid":25345,"like":25,"dislike":348,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"b91bb936c14a7fcd514c8b7ab9e8ee2c84697522","tid":2340983,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T03:34:46.000Z","msg":"蘋果正開發&ldquo;蘋果汽車&rdquo;，已經是一個公開的秘密了！雖然進展過程非常緩慢，但是近日又越來越多消息證明，蘋果汽車馬上要與大眾見面了！<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcrawl.ws.126.net%2Fimg%2Fe0591f2524ddac2750afdcce49f570c8.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcrawl.ws.126.net%252Fimg%252Fe0591f2524ddac2750afdcce49f570c8.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=f5746f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  到目前為止，我們並未從蘋果官方處窺視到蘋果汽車的長相，不過，近日，外媒LetsGoDigital根據蘋果申請的一系列專利圖，繪製出了有關&ldquo;Apple Car&rdquo;的3D 概念渲染圖。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  從渲染圖來看，該車在外觀上有很大突破，整體呈簡約高級風，車身線條流暢，車前有一個顯眼的蘋果Logo。據設計師描述，寬闊視野和獨特流線型車身，會是Apple Car最顯著的特點。此外，該車在安全性上也十分有保障。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcrawl.ws.126.net%2Fimg%2Fdb8856695c0905380e143944a277b67d.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcrawl.ws.126.net%252Fimg%252Fdb8856695c0905380e143944a277b67d.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=fbe0ced7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  當然，作為一款電動汽車，性能抗打也是最關鍵的因素之一。根據此前網上曝光的信息來看，蘋果汽車將會採用&ldquo;單電芯&rdquo;電池設計，使其能夠優化電池組內部的空間，並增加汽車續航里程。據知情人士稱，該電池或將是磷酸鐵鋰(LFP)化學材料，與目前特斯拉中國製造的Model 3是同款。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcrawl.ws.126.net%2Fimg%2Fcebcf568bca5580b4f11578e73e0d0c0.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcrawl.ws.126.net%252Fimg%252Fcebcf568bca5580b4f11578e73e0d0c0.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=a906b0d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  話說回來，如果蘋果汽車量產上市，不知道價格會怎樣。"},{"pid":"82ac2b63cea1a0c1933faac8def72cf454dae19c","tid":2340983,"uid":1845,"like":290,"dislike":2,"score":288,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T03:36:41.000Z","msg":"滑鼠？"},{"pid":"7deeae6ee661666a17b626428f7b98dd6c1ecd27","tid":2340983,"uid":131101,"like":250,"dislike":6,"score":244,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T03:36:42.000Z","msg":"好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77c87b2f83b23eaab6415afb4d621916e501b44","tid":2340983,"uid":160373,"like":379,"dislike":4,"score":375,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T03:37:56.000Z","msg":"可能四個轆會分別收費"},{"pid":"9223fbaff13bb40a27429d425a24db70bbbdf4a9","tid":2340983,"uid":54823,"like":330,"dislike":3,"score":327,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T03:39:52.000Z","msg":"咁似隻mouse 嘅"},{"pid":"27c33e630942b0e48f06f6d58e78c5951ca3b3dd","tid":2340983,"uid":110568,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T03:40:46.000Z","msg":"fake news 多"},{"pid":"cbcf71a376869526377a75eaae0c2d80ac12e502","tid":2340983,"uid":181789,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T03:41:42.000Z","msg":"加返個apple care 先啦"},{"pid":"987358802c395f165b644c1e2e31facb698f3e7f","tid":2340983,"uid":385412,"like":241,"dislike":3,"score":238,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T03:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0bDUBP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0bDUBP.jpg&h=7e5f90d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個叉電位會唔會喺車底<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8baf416257b1fb2ec7d84865fcbeae20d1e2b50b","tid":2340983,"uid":186997,"like":445,"dislike":0,"score":445,"quote":{"pid":"987358